Quote:  I am sticking to the 'bun' technique for silage-making this year. The main reason that I am sticking with buns for silage is pasture damage. I have a feeling that I'll end up by having two pits, concrete and all and still make buns to be fed out before the ground conditions become soft. [bun clamp]
